'''Nationwide Windscreens Services Ltd (NWS)''' was founded in 2006 so that independent windscreen replacement companies, by forming an association within NWS, could be part of an organisation capable of serving customers with UK National requirements.

Originally located in [[Poole]], NWS headquarters moved to [[Quorn, Leicestershire|Quorn]], [[Leicestershire]] in 2008. The central location, with easy access to the UK motorway network system, rail systems and within easy reach of [[East Midlands Airport|East Midland]] and [[Birmingham Airport|Birmingham]] airports, is advantageous to members and customers.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.natwin.co.uk/ | title=Home | publisher=Nationwide Windscreen Services | accessdate=26 September 2012}}</ref>

