'''Opplysningskontoret for egg og kjøtt''' ("The Information Office for Eggs and Meat") is a Norwegian private organisation which seeks to provide information and help on behalf of the Norwegian [[meat industry]]. It among other things receives 69 million [[Norwegian krone]] in annual subsidies from the [[Government of Norway]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nationen.no/2011/01/21/landbruk/opplysningskontoret_for_egg_og_kjott/framtiden_i_vare_hender/6395349/ |title=Vil legge ned opplysningskontoret for kjøtt |work=[[Nationen]] |date=22 January 2011 |accessdate=22 January 2011 |archivedate=22 January 2011 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vvnIIvMj}}</ref>

